Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Suzuki Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak SMA kelas 2, umur 16 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Yusuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enam bulan lalu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku menembak Tani, cowok incaranku\Nyang duduk di sebelahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami pun mulai pacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Nabe, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Taira-Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian barengan dari pagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menikmati kehidupan sekolah yang seru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bahagia bareng teman-teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sejujurnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beneran, sedikit saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak sabar banget
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ingin melakukan kegiatan ala pacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}You and I are Polar Opposites\NSeason 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya mereka lagi foto-foto, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak kelas tiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin buat kenang-kenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya kita bakal bocor di belakang, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak mau muka asliku yang belum diedit\Nmasuk ke medsos orang tak dikenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat tuh, adik kelas cewek lewat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jahat banget, sih!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, pose peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kooperatif banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Azuma, sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu, kamu berteman sama kakak kelas itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak kenal, tuh.\NSiapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suasana dan cara mereka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengganggu kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengingatkan aku sama teman-temannya kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi anehnya, aku lumayan suka suasananya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu, soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang sih mereka mengajak kita ngobrol,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalau boleh jujur,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu cuma sebatas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cowok yang lagi iseng saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, cowok iseng kayak gitu malah seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatimu lapang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Servis yang bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Servis yang mantap, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}HENING…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}MENOLEH…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyangkut!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakar Pengambil Bola.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah biasa, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, ini Kelas 7 lawan Kelas omong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang lagi unggul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tim mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab gih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, kamu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan aku,\Naku belum pernah ngobrol sama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin deg-degan banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kroket kantin memang paling enak\Nhabis olahraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhir-akhir ini lagi ada kabar baik, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kelihatan semangat banget\Nbelakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omonganmu seakan-akan\Nsebelumnya aku penyakitan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya pacar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pas liburan musim panas kemarin sempat\Nada yang PDKT,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ujungnya nihil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semenjak itu enggak ada apa-apa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak paham\Nsama romansa musim panas kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya kelar\Nsebelum aku sempat bilang apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu enggak kirim balasan aneh-aneh, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dimaafkan, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma kamu yang rugi di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cueki semua pesannya\Nyang cuma basa-basi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantap juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada dicueki,\Nmending diblokir sekalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Blokir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hajar saja pakai batako sekalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secara fisik, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gara-gara kamu bilang\Nselalu suka cowok berengsek,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi khawatir banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak tahu kenapa, deh. Masih jadi misteri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok malah kedengaran santai banget?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi makan apa, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, apaan, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kakak kelas tiga yang tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kroket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Azu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bodoh banget, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Layani saja,\Nnanti mereka juga berhenti ganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mending dicueki saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Palingan mereka bakal gagal ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jujur saja,\Ndaripada dibenci terang-terangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mending digituin, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya dia masih kepikiran\Nsoal tadi, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gini, lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka cuma kaget gara-gara kamu\Ntiba-tiba mengajak ngobrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu jarang banget ngobrol\Nsama mereka, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak semua orang kayak gitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paham apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan kenapa Azuma selalu\Nmenarik perhatian cowok berengsek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya ada di "kecepatan awal".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau orang yang berhati-hati
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}PDKT selangkah demi selangkah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada juga orang kayak\Nkakak-kakak kelas tadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang langsung menerobos masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menerobos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya pas ada yang menerobos masuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu enggak marah, tapi malah menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya kamu mikir itu hal yang wajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harusnya marah kalau ada\Nyang memperlakukanmu seenaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkatnya, karena kamu terlalu\Nmaklum dan toleran,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu malah enggak sabar\Nmenghadapi orang yang PDKT-nya pelan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemahaman metaforamu cepat juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, memangnya begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua cowok yang tebar pesona di awal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti berengsek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa cowok baik-baik itu membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya sih begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, sama kayak susah\Njalan jauh pakai gigi rendah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang yang langsung ngegas di awal\Nbiasanya enggak bakal bertahan lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak usah pakai perumpamaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah makin susah dimengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tadi aku cuma mau\Npamer kefasihanku saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya santai banget, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berpikir matang-matang\Ndan mendekat secara perlahan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku melakukan itu, apa aku bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}punya hubungan kayak Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak mungkin, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ngegas banget mengejar Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai bingung kapan harus ikut campur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak gitu, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... Aku PDKT\Nselangkah demi selangkah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius, deh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Malah bikin makin kepo.\N- Mereka lagi ngobrol tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan Tani suka sama Suzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku juga penasaran soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, ayolah, kasih tahu kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan, teman-teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rencananya aku mau nanya itu nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang bulan Desember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalanan ramai, dan bernuansa meriah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagu Natal terdengar di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat semua orang larut\Ndalam suasana gembira ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setelah kelar ujian akhir\Ndan upacara penutupan sekolah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Liburan musim dingin sudah di depan mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kalian lengah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}liburannya bakal berlalu sekejap mata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, liburan musim dingin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kerja bagus, Semuanya!\N- Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki dan yang lain\Nsudah sepenuhnya masuk mode liburan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelas 7 lagi pesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kayak Bajak Laut Topi Jerami saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agak seram, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau ayam goreng?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Promosi macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan keluarkan makanan\Nyang bikin tangan berminyak, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita enggak bisa makannya sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan remehkan banyaknya barang bawaan\Nkami habis ujian akhir, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mau langsung pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau gitu, kayaknya kita\Nbaru ketemu lagi tahun depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga. Setelah dipikir-pikir,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bakal lumayan lama\Nsampai kita masuk sekolah lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa tahun depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat Tahun Baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat Tahun Baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini terakhir kalinya di tahun ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa rencana kalian\Nbuat liburan musim dingin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargaku selalu pergi ke rumah nenek
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buat merayakan Tahun Baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau gitu, kita enggak bisa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke kuil bareng dong pas Tahun Baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku pesan piza tanggal 24 atau 25,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sinterklas Yamada yang bakal antar, enggak?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masuk kerja di dua hari itu,\Njadi mungkin saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu kerja paruh waktu di kedai piza?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, awas saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bakal mengamuk kalau\Nkamu sampai pesan piza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan remehkan padatnya kerjaan\Npas Natal, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti dia\Nenggak ada acara kencan pas Natal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bakal di rumah saja pas Natal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum memutuskan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi idemu boleh juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bakal minta rekomendasi\Nresep kue dari Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Koki Kawasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu punya acara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}buat Natal nanti?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu kita harus ngapain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tanya aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak usah terlalu dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan kue sambil tukar kado saja\Nsudah cukup, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, itu kekanak-kanakan banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, gitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan telan mentah-mentah omonganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selama liburan musim dingin.\Ncuma kerja paruh waktu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sif kerjaku juga enggak banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Palingan aku cuma bakal main gim doang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu enggak terlalu buruk, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau pada lagi senggang\Npas liburan musim dingin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita main bareng, yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ke luar kota pas Tahun Baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, mau gimana lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, anggota Klub Pulang Cepat,\Nhabis ini kita jalan-jalan, yuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dadakan banget!\N- Kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya aku masih ingin nongkrong bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita lihat rumah-rumah mewah\Ndi atas bukit, yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aktivitas macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti aku ada kerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga ada ekskul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lewat sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berasa kayak lagi jalan pulang sekolah bareng.\NSeru banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berasa balik jadi anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu masih muda, kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa kecilnya Azuma telat datangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini, lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata tempatnya bagus banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap tahun memang spektakuler.\NNamanya iluminasi perumahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir, ini pertama kalinya aku\Nke tempat yang bernuansa Natal tahun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walaupun ini cuma area\Nperumahan biasa, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya kamu sempat ke pasar Natal\Ndi dekat Pecinan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lihat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja.\NCuma aku yang tahu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak kayak kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak bakal nanya hal\Nyang merusak suasana...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di depan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma bercanda, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasih tahu aku kalau ada kemajuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, belum sampai ke tahap itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita bisa double date,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti bakal seru, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semangat banget sampai rasanya mual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senyumku enggak bisa berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat Tahun Baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga bakal begini jadinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melakukan\Nlebih banyak hal bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sih enggak keberatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dilihat lagi bareng aku?\Ntapi apa dia enggak takut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, dia kayaknya cuek saja\Nsama omongan atau kebencian orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia beda banget sama aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau mampir ke toko buku sebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duluan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa tahun depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir,\Nmemang sudah ada tanda-tandanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya aku terlalu kelihatan jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah sering ditolak, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa malah Azuma yang kelihatan\Nkayak orang habis ditolak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kami akrab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa malah aku yang menolak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anggap saja aku enggak pernah omong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak harus pergi sekarang, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara itu, Suzuki dan Tani...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus ngapain?\NBalik saja, yuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak saat itu, mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi canggung banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}BERHENTI…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku ingin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bareng sama kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dan bikin kue bareng.\N- Makan kue bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan begitulah,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}liburan musim dingin pun dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa Tani boleh main ke sini tanggal 24?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari itu Ibu ada sif kerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu enggak bakal bisa siapkan\Nmakan malam yang pantas buat dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia datangnya siang, kok...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan pulang sebelum malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu, Ibu yakin kamu sudah paham,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi jangan sampai terbawa suasana\Ncuma gara-gara enggak ada orang di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak waktu kakakmu dan teman-temannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}banting stik gim...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai memecahkan pajangan kucing keramik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak bakal, kok!\NKami cuma mau bikin kue bareng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah. Bersenang-senanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari Natal,\Ndan cuma ada kami berdua di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sih...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perkembangan asmara yang mutlak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mari kita beli...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahan-bahan dan peralatannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita beli loyang tar yang paling besar saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti proporsi kuenya berubah, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhubung ini hari spesial,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ayo pakai alas piring ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau yang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belanja bareng begini
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya agak surealis, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berasa kayak pasangan yang tinggal seatap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa. Aku senang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin ada daun bawang\Nyang nongol dari kantong belanjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau roti baget yang nongol\Ndari kantong kertas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kumasukkan ke kulkas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma merasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani lucu banget pas lagi menghancurkan kukis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan meledek, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ratakan bagian pinggirnya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin begini saja sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus jernihkan pikiran sebentar.\NAku mikirnya kejauhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}TERSENTUH…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau dipanaskan dulu\Nmakanan yang kita beli tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja. Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal kayak gini pernah terjadi sebelumnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya butuh dua jam sampai selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proses mendinginkannya lumayan lama, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi agak bingung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barusan kami ciuman, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami beneran ciuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku mengidam-idamkan ciuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang kayak di film-film putri Disney...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku enggak sangka
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami malah enggak sengaja ciuman kayak tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan aku cuma salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo lakukan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya yang tadi enggak masuk hitungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku habis makan ayam panggang, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, aku yang minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya enggak ada orang di rumah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai nanti malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu lagi ngapain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu di rumah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan urusanmu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bakal di rumah seharian?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ada barang yang ketinggalan.\NHabis ini aku pergi, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu. Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu nyebelin banget, deh, hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah! Selamat bersenang-senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hiperaktif banget, sih. Jijik, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin kaget setengah mati saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya aku sapa dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepatu siapa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa lagi kali ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu dompetmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu kelihatan agak marah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita coba lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuenya jadi bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada waktu buat belanja
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bikinnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita menghabiskan kuenya terlalu cepat, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya esensi memasak itu ada di prosesnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia! Waktunya tukar kado Natal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ada kado buat kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, masa sih!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mirip sama kadoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya tanganmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selalu dingin, kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku pilih ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kelihatan cukup pemilih soal fesyen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku sempat ragu lama banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat! Manis banget, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natal pertama kami berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walaupun semuanya terasa agak janggal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak lama lagi, lagu Natal di kota
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bakal berganti jadi suara petikan koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apanya yang lucu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Habisnya...\N- Bukan apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini aku dengar\Nada yang bersenandung senada petikan koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyadari kalau orang yang kita cintai,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga balas mencintai kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah momen paling membahagiakan di dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ciuman itu sendiri\Nsebenarnya enggak terlalu penting...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jujur saja, aku cuma sok tegar, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang mana yang bakal dihitung\Nsebagai ciuman pertama kita hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}UHUK…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SAMPAI JUMPA DI EPISODE BERIKUTNYA…
